# Mr. Bonzo Beats — project rules

- Before structural or UI work, read `architecture.md` and `guardrails.md`. Follow `AGENTS.md`.
- **i18n:** every new string in both `src/i18n/en.ts` and `src/i18n/el.ts`; `.astro` defaults must match English.
- **Links:** use `src/config/links.ts` for social/store URLs (Discord, TikTok, Spotify, Beatstars, etc.).
- **Visual FX:** do not reintroduce full-page custom cursor or film grain unless the user explicitly asks. Navbar-only `#nav-hover-ring` is the only custom pointer FX.
- **Releases:** keep newest-first sorting; pin new albums in `pinnedReleases` in `src/pages/index.astro` when API/scrape lag.
- **Save:** prefer `npm run save -- "conventional message"` (alias `npm run git-save`). The script always updates docs stamps/Save log — still edit prose when behaviour changes.
- **CSP:** any new third-party script needs CSP updates in `BaseLayout.astro` and a note in `architecture.md`.
- Do not put `/* */` comments inside HTML tags in `.astro` files.
